dt-bindings: pwm: stm32: Add #pwm-cells

STM32 Timers support generic 3 cells PWM bindings to encode PWM number,
period and polarity as defined in pwm.txt.

Fixes: cd9a99c2f8e8 ("dt-bindings: pwm: Add STM32 bindings")
